text: Hu ure ieldran ealne þisne middangeard on þreo todældon.
Hu Ninus, Asiria cyning, ongon monna ærest ricsian on þiosan middangearde; & hu Sameramis his cwen feng to þæm rice æfter him mid micelre reðnesse & wrænnesse.
Hu þæt heofenisce fyr forbærnde þæt lond on þæm wæron þa twa byrig on getimbred, Sodome & Gomorre.
Hu Thelesci & Ciarsæthi þa leode him betweonum wunnon.

Hu Ioseph se ryhtwisa mon ahredde Egypta folc æt þæm seofan geara miclan hungre mid his wisdome; & hu hie siþþan ealra hiora wæstma þone fiftan dæl ælce geare heora cyninge to gafole gesellað æfter his gesetnesse.
Hu on Achaie wearþ micel flod on Ambictiones dagum þæs cyninges.
Hu Moyses lædde Israhela folc from Egyptum ofer þone Readan Sæ.
Hu on Egyptum wurdon on anre niht L monna ofslagen from hiora agnum sunum; & hu Bosiridis se cyning het don to geblote ealle þa cuman þe hiene gesohtan; & ymbe monegra oþerra folca gewinn.
Hu Cretense & Athaniense, Creca leode, him betweonum wunnon.

Hu Uesoges, Egypta cyning, wolde him to geteon ge þone suðdæl, þæt is Asia, ge þone norþdæl, þæt sint Sciþþie; & hu ii æþelingas wurdon afliemed of Sciþþium; & ymbe þa wif þe mon Amozenas het; & ymbe þa Gotan, þe him fore andredan ge Pirrus se reþa creca cyning, ge se mæra Alexander, ge Iulius se casere.
Hu Elena, þæs cyninges wif, wearð genumen on Læcedomonia þære byrig; & hu Eneas se cyning gefor mid fierde on Italie.

Hu Sardanopolus wæs se siþemesta cyning in Asiria, ond hu hiene beswac Arbatus his ealdormon; & hu þa wifmen bysmredan hiora weras, þe hie fleon woldon; ond hu se argeotere geworhte anes fearres onlicnesse þæm æþelinge.
Hu Pelopensium & Atheniensium þa folc him betweonum wunnon.
Hu Læcedemonie & Mesiane him betweonum wunnon for hiora mægdena offrunga.
Hu Orosius sæde þæt ure Dryhten þone ærestan mon swiþe ryhtne & swiþe godne gesceope; & ymbe þa feower onwealdas þises middangeardes.
Hu Remus & Romulus þa gebroþor getimbredan Romeburg on Italiam.
Hu Romulus & Brutus mid hwelcum mane hie gehalgedon Roma.
Hu Romane & Sabine him betweonum <wunnon>; & hu Cirus wearð ofslagen on Sciþþium.
Hu Cambisis se cyning forseah þa Egyptiescan diofolgield; & ymbe Dariuses gewinn & Xersis, & Leoniþan.
Hu Romanum wearð an wundor oþiewed, swelce se heofon burne.
Hu Sicilia leode wæron him betweonum winnende.
Hu Romane besæton Ueiorum þa burg x winter; & hu Galliæ of Senno abræcan Romeburg.
Hu sio bysmerlice sibb & facenlice wearð betweonum Læcedemonium & Persum.
Hu on Achaie wearð eorþbeofung.
Hu se micla monncwealm wearð on Rome on twegra consula dæge; & hu Marcus Curtius besceat on þa ginigendan eorþan.
Hu Galliæ oferhergodon Romana lond on iii mila to þære byrg.
Hu Cartaina ærendwracan comon to Rome & him frið gebudon.
Hu Romane & Latine wunnon him betweonum; & hu an nunne wearþ cuca bebyrged.
Hu Alexander se cyning wonn wið Romane, þæs maran Alexandres eam; & hu Philippus, þæs maran Alexandres fæder, feng to Mæcedonia rice, ond he him geceas Bizantium þa burg.
Hu Caudenes Furculus sio stow wearþ swiþe widmære for Romana bismere.
Hu se mæra Alexander feng to Mæcedonia rice; & hu he het sumne sumne biscep secgan on his gewill hwa his fæder wære; & hu he Darius þone cyning oferwon; & hu he self wearð mid atre acweald.
Hu under ii consulum woldon iiii þa strengstan þeoda Romane oferwinnan; & hu se micla cwealm gewearð on Rome; & hu hi him heton gefeccean to Escolapius þone scinlacan mid þære <scinlacan> nædran.
Hu under ii consulum wurdon Somnite & Gallie of Senno þære byrig Romanum wiþerwinnan; ond hu Alexandres heretogan heora lif on unsibbe geendedon æfter Alexandres deaþe.
Hu Tarentine gesawan Romano scipa on ðæm sæ <irnan>, þa hie plegedon on hiora theatrum.
Hu þa monegan yflan wundor wurdon on Rome.
Hu mon geseah weallan blod of eorþan & rinan meolc of heofonum.
Hu on Romane becom micel moncwealm; & hu Caperrone sio nunne wearþ ahangen; ond hu þa burgleode on Cartaina <bleotan> men hiora godum .
Hu Himeolco, Cartaina cyning, for mid fierde on Siciliae; ond hu Hanna an mon wæs onwaldes giernende; ond hu Cartaine hierdon þæt se mæra Alexander hæfde abrocen Tirum þa burg.

Hu Sicilia folc & Pena wunnon him betweonum; & hu Romane besæton Hannibalan, Pena cyning; & hu Calatinus se consul for mid fierde to Camerinan, Sicilia byrg; & hu Punice gesetton eft þone ealdan Hannibalan þæt he mid scipum wiþ Romane wunne; & hu Romane foron on Affrice mid þrim hunda scipa & mid XXX; & hu Regulus se consul ofslog þa ungemetlican nædran; & hu Regulus gefeaht wiþ iii Pena cyningas on anum gefeohte; & hu Enilius se consul for on Affricam mid iii hunde scipe; & hu ii consulas foran mid iii hunde scipa on Affrice; & hu Cotta se consul <oferhergede> Sicilie; ond <hu> on þriora consula dæge com Hasterbal se niwa cyning to Libeum þæm iglande; & hu Claudius se consul for eft on Punice; & hu Gaius se consul for on Affrice & on þæm sæ forwearð; & hu Lutatia se consul for on Affrice mid iii hunde scipa.

Hu se ungemetlica fyrbryne wearþ on Rome; & hu Gallie wurdon Romanum wiðerwearde; & hu Sardinie wunnon on Romane, swa hie Pene gelærdon; & hu Orosius sæde þæt he wære cumen to ðæm godan tidan þe Romane eft fore gulpon; & hu Gallie wunnon on Romane, & Pene on oþre healfe; & hu ii consulas fuhton on Gallium; & hu monig wundor wæron gesewene; & hu Claudius se consul ofslog Gallia XXX m.
Hu Hannibal, Pena cyning, besæt Saguntum, Ispania burg; & hu Hannibal abræc ofer Perenei þa beorgas; & hu Scipia se consul gefeaht on Ispanium; & hu monige wundor gewurdon on þære tide.
Hu Hannibal beswac ii consulas on heora gefeohte; & hu Romane him gesetton tictator & Scipian to consule; & hu Romane sendon Lucius þone consul on Gallie mid iii legian.

Hu Marcellus se consul for mid sciphere on Sicilie; & hu Hannibal gefeaht wiþ Marcellus þone consul iii dagas; & hu Hannibal bestæl on Marcellus þone consul & hine ofslog; & hu Asterbal, Hannibales broðor, for of Ispanium on Italie; & hu Cartainum wearþ frið aliefed from Scipian þæm consule.

Hu Romane æfterre gewinn & <Punica> wearð geendod; & hu Sempronius se consul wearð ofslagen on Ispania; & hu Philippus, Mæcedonia cyng, ofslog Romano ærenddracan; ond hu þæt Mæcedonisce gewin gewearð; & hu Enilius se consul oferwon Perseus þone cyning.
Hu Romanum wearþ se mæste ege from Sceltiferin, Ispania folce.
Hu þæt þridde gewinn wearþ geendod Romano & Cartaina.
Hu Orosius spræc ymbe Romano gielp, hu hie monega folc oferwunnon; & hu hie monege cyningas beforan hiora triumphan wið Rome weard drifon.

Hu on anum geare wurdon þa twa byrg toworpena, Cartaina & Corinthum; & hu Ueriatus se hierde ongon ricsian on Ispanium; & hu Claudius se consul gefliemde Gallie; & hu Mantius se consul genam friþ wið Ispanie; & hu Brutus se consul ofslog Ispania LX M; & hu an cild wearþ geboren on Rome.
Hu Romane sendon Scipian on Ispanie mid fierde; & hu Craccus se consul wonn wið þa oðre consulas, oþ hi hine ofslogon; & hu þa þeowas <wunnan> wiþ þa hlafordas.

Hu Lucinius se consul, se þe eac wæs Romano ieldesta biscep, for mid fierde angean Aristonocuse þæm cyninge; & hu Antiochus, Asia cyning, wilnade Partha onwaldes; & hu Scipia, se betsta Romano þegn, mænde his earfeþa to Romano weotum; & hu Eþna fyr upp afleow.
Hu Romane heton eft getimbran Cartaina; & hu se consul Metellus oferwon þa wicingas.
Hu Fauius se consul ofercom Betuitusan, Gallia cyning.
Hu Romane <wunnon> wiþ Geoweorþan, Numedia cyninge.
Hu Romane ongunnon unsibbe him betweonum up ahebban on þæm fiftan geare þe Marius wæs consul.
Hu ofer ealle Italie wearð ungeferlic unsibb on þæm siextan geare þe Iulius se casere wæs consul.
Hu Romane sendon Sillan þone consul ongean Metredatis, Partha cyning.
Hu Romane sealdon Gaiuse þæm consule seofon legian; & hu Iulius besæt Tarquatus, Pompeiuses ladteow, on anum fæstenne; & hu Iulius gefeaht wið Ptholomeus iiia.
Hu Octauianus feng to Romano onwalde hiora unwillum.
Hu Octauianus se <casere> betynde Ianes duru.
Hu sume Ispanie wæron Agustuse wiþerwinnan.
Hu Orosius wæs sprecende ymbe þa iiii onwaldas þara feower heafedrica þisses middangeardes.
Hu Tiberius feng to Romano anwalde se casere æfter Agustuse.
Hu Gaius wearþ casere iiii gear.
Hu Tiberius Claudius feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Nero feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Galua feng to Romano anwalde se casere.
Hu Uespasianus feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Titus feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Domitianus, Tituses broðor, feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Nerfa feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Adrianus feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Pompeius feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Marcus Antonius feng to Romano anwalde mid Aureliuse his breðer.
Hu Lucius feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Seuerus feng to Romano rice.
Hu his sunu feng to rice, Antonius.
Hu Marcus feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Aurelius feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Maximus feng to Romano anwalde.
Hu Gordianus feng to Romano rice.
Hu Philippus feng to Romano rice.
Hu Decius feng to Romano rice.
Hu Gallus feng to Romano rice.
Hu Romane gesetton ii caseras.
Hu Claudius feng to Romano rice.
Hu Aurelius feng to Romana rice.
Hu Tacitus feng to Romana rice.
Hu Probus feng to Romana rice.
Hu Carus feng to Romana rice.
Hu Dioclitianus feng to Romana rice.
Hu Constantinus feng to Romana onwalde mid his ii broþrum.
Hu Iuuinianus feng to Romana rice.
Hu Ualentinianus feng to Romana rice.
Hu Ualens feng to Romana rice.
Hu Gratianus feng to Romana rice; & hu Brettanie namon Maximianum him to casere ofer his willan.
Hu Theodosius feng to Romana onwalde; & hu Ualentinianus feng eft to rice.
Hu Archadius feng to Romana rice, & Honorius to þam westrice.
Hu God gedyde Romanum his mildsunge.
